[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Checking classifier mapping**\n\nI’m thinking about the classifier no_aop and how it maps to different formats. I wonder if there's a hyphen version for Gradle with no-aop, while Maven might have it listed differently as no_aop. I think it would be useful to check the central listing to verify how these different build tools represent the same classifier. It feels important to be consistent here, so I’ll make sure to gather that information.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0089db3286031404016a3ee4a539c48194be3dcf9b5f953742\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqPuSnDzTmjEZQ4Ru27vciNiUJ7ir2hJxI2rahrX8uNSOuzb9TWgtd5GNZPd_ozD0-aBdUYB54Vo50FNRuPpuPl865CZHNWpmd6Nk-W6MNQx9oQsuGhPcWKQDtzBBx9PJsKyTUeceA004yAQrIjiT06E0BQ6IH3Z3hn3GYz_6F8DwNddsIJFKhykoBlxKNT_zEoSI_whhjNXSbO9_MaNKfP7mQTLdyJ8uUPpCzQkZ8dua8c3Wrt-udGjfD8jnj_p4LFCOSs7hIO6QY6ilgJvsKz28OkJRY2qft-robCz20qiIr0Odow-AKrnewq8W8VGBR4pAksXF-EMNrwzk88XKU9VbovMp4CnkbXVbVphOb3X_809FAy7lNqv5dh2_1em6riryg4ZQeqes8rn4Z9X3b4BCrMpFCeLFY8BCam3WsCVTyK3blUbA1okYbPwyHJezL_sVYmYf6MoCEz7dlRwQZvVkLCjVs2Sx3LzTSph_TyhHoCaZ5aELeiL62T1Aj2_-08GzUSg1AY6RC246NWmcy72vtcj4HyLhTEuAyStonFJK2W9L1CXq8gB3zIGBDtzJHjjl_89lag0NV8lFrr5rve0hgKP6vCdE_37lBzg3CAkxg1Gy5YHitioAcZ21DHM_vd5Zp3DqkyET9jr5dW4vhjgKhTjlVFTxZbh1XMmORgPQCaatu0muNCAI3XL5C4x9kudeG6HLWf_k-47NL22wtC9X_xAbl40nIX7jRPfMsKPqKi9NPdWj78aMArt9WdojRH-BrPOd95bdlNmsXbyhrL7nZQ8pPzI9OwP1K4NBkagIl6sh0fcvm3TxQgMeY77tpmRqMFqvM-xLRKYMeKRVv3iNTqJ00lbEqite3A63W8aHp_4LBBVUWD84d4ToA46zYLGWjGyDaoEuLAoVnJDkZ-gW_jUlKIeZAr-0yNOJhY6pkqVR-OLIAYKQjgvEAVsiv5dvylnO4ESgYA-MN4eLUKM4dFO-eh2Tp8MuwLb6MbqKRqEHBIdT-TZS-Bw3_JTZvhVX6bgzxpgwkOTy4NzjXwtO9tOjt5206G7HnDRpsH3pOnpTnEEo3YuZ0Eu_pLSmilICD\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Checking classifier mapping**\\n\\nI’m thinking about the classifier no_aop and how it maps to different formats. I wonder if there's a h